asset.title: VonZipper : Imaginarium : Behind the Scenes
asset.description: In an attempt to photograph low-light surfing in a unique way - VonZipper and commercial fashion photographer Michael Muller collaborated to shoot their Imaginarium concept utilizing custom, waterproof 1,200-watt strobes, four surfers, and a crew of over 20 people. We caught up with Mike to get his thoughts on the end result.
asset.author: VonZipper
